    <div class="content">
        <section class="info-section">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>
                Welcome to Smart Healthcare, where we use advanced Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN) to detect skin cancer from uploaded images. Our application provides a quick and reliable way to analyze your skin conditions with the latest AI technology.
            </p>
            <p>
                By uploading an image of your skin, you can get a preliminary assessment of potential issues, which can then be further evaluated by a healthcare professional.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="upload-section">
            <h2>Upload an Image for Detection</h2>
            <form id="uploadForm" action="/api/predict" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                <input type="file" name="image" accept="image/*" required>
                <button type="submit">CHECK YOUR SKIN NOW</button>
            </form>
        </section>
    </div>

